data.description: Welcome to this 4-bedroom, 2.5-bathroom, plus loft home nestled in the heart of a gated Westbridge community. Built in 2020 with Centex Builder!  You are greeted with high ceiling foyer reaching up to the second level with an upgraded wrought iron spindle staircase. The main living area has an open concept with the kitchen and dining room. The kitchen has lots of storage including the side island cabinets (custom garbage cabinet and slider drawers), kitchen island seating, 42" tall upper cabinets, stainless steel appliances, closet pantry, and granite countertops. There is a bedroom downstairs which can serve multiple uses and a half bath. The entire first floor of this property is tile including the extra bedroom! Upstairs you will find an open loft, two bedrooms, laundry room, and primary bedroom. The primary bedroom is separate from other rooms offering privacy. The primary bathroom has a double vanity, linen closet, and oversized walk-in shower. The second bathroom has double vanity, and bathtub/shower. The back lanai is covered, and the lot has ample space to make your own. Home has smart door technology, smart thermostat, 30 AMP power inlet for generator, built-in WiFi access points on both levels, floor outlets in living room and loft! Culligan water filter and water softener already installed in the home! Wesbridge community has two gated entrances and low $45 monthly HOA! In addition, it is located near the new I-75 Overpass exit and walking distance to schools to Wesley Chapel Elementary, Thomas E Wightman Middle, and Wesley Chapel High School. The community offers pool, splash pad, playground, and tot lot. Neighborhood is conveniently located near shops, restaurants, Wiregrass Mall, Krates, and more! No flood zone.
